  "body": "Probably for another time, but it may be worth trying to remove explicit subcommands instantiation, setup proper [factories](https://picocli.info/#_custom_factory) for those classes and then set the subcommands field in the BesuCommand class with INHERIT scope. That way we won't need to explicitly set the versionProvider and mixinStandardHelpOptions everywhere (ref: https://github.com/remkop/picocli/issues/1164)\r\n\r\nAs per comments on this PR:\r\nhttps://github.com/hyperledger/besu/pull/3577",
